  m_text: "D\u1EBE M\xC8N PHI\xCAU L\u01AFU K\xDD\nDCGHUT\n\nGI\u1EA2NG VI\xCAN H\u01AF\u1EDANG
    D\u1EAAN\nNguy\u1EC5n Tr\xED \u0110\u1ECBnh\n\nTHI\u1EBET K\u1EBE GAME\nNguy\u1EC5n
    Song To\xE0n\nNguy\u1EC5n \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\n\nTHI\u1EBET K\u1EBE M\xC0N CH\u01A0I\nNguy\u1EC5n
    \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\nB\xF9i Ho\xE0ng Duy\n\nTHI\u1EBET K\u1EBE H\u1EC6 TH\u1ED0NG
    GAME\n\u0110\u1EB7ng Hi\u1EC7p Th\xE0nh\nNguy\u1EC5n T\u1EA5n Kh\u1EA3i\nNguy\u1EC5n
    \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\nB\xF9i Ho\xE0ng Duy\n\nTHI\u1EBET K\u1EBE C\u1ED0T TRUY\u1EC6N
    GAME\nNguy\u1EC5n Song To\xE0n\n\nTHI\u1EBET K\u1EBE GAMEPLAY\n\u0110\u1EB7ng
    Hi\u1EC7p Th\xE0nh\nNguy\u1EC5n T\u1EA5n Kh\u1EA3i\nNguy\u1EC5n \u0110\xECnh
    Th\xE1i\nB\xF9i Ho\xE0ng Duy\n\nT\xC1C GI\u1EA2 M\xD4I TR\u01AF\u1EDCNG\nNguy\u1EC5n
    \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\nB\xF9i Ho\xE0ng Duy\n\nT\xC1C GI\u1EA2 NH\xC2N V\u1EACT\nNguy\u1EC5n
    Song To\xE0n\nNguy\u1EC5n Tu\u1EA5n Ki\u1EC7t\n\nANIMATOR\nNguy\u1EC5n Song To\xE0n\nNguy\u1EC5n
    Tu\u1EA5n Ki\u1EC7t\n\u0110\u1EB7ng Hi\u1EC7p Th\xE0nh\nNguy\u1EC5n T\u1EA5n
    Kh\u1EA3i\n\nT\xC1C GI\u1EA2 \xDD T\u01AF\u1EDENG\nNguy\u1EC5n Song To\xE0n\nNguy\u1EC5n
    \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\nNguy\u1EC5n Tu\u1EA5n Ki\u1EC7t\n\nTHI\u1EBET K\u1EBE \xC2M
    THANH\n\u0110\u1EB7ng Hi\u1EC7p Th\xE0nh\nNguy\u1EC5n \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\n\nC\xC1C
    NH\xC0 THI\u1EBET K\u1EBE\nNguy\u1EC5n Song To\xE0n\nNguy\u1EBFn Tu\u1EA5n Ki\u1EC7t\nNguy\u1EC5n
    \u0110\xECnh Th\xE1i\nB\xF9i Ho\xE0ng Duy\n\u0110\u1EB7ng Hi\u1EC7p Th\xE0nh\nNguy\u1EC5n
    T\u1EA5n Kh\u1EA3i\n\n\n\n"
